BonfyreCompress — family-aware compression engine

Usage:
  bonfyre-compress train <dir> [--dict-out F]    Train zstd dictionary
  bonfyre-compress pack <in> <out> [--dict D]    Compress file
  bonfyre-compress unpack <in> <out> [--dict D]  Decompress file
  bonfyre-compress family <dir> [--out F]        Pack entire family
  bonfyre-compress savings <dir>                 Report savings
